imdb.plot outline: FilAm Jams on FilAm TV Television program (Digital 31.3) aims to provide viewers with an in-depth look into the world music art scene and the role Filipino Americans play in shaping it. Hosted by Loren Burgos and Quark Henares. Viewers even get an in-depth look the lives of various musicians and their artistic process in creating original material. With the spotlight focused on new artists overflowing with promise and potential, the show is a platform for them to showcase their talents to the Filipino American community. A segment hosted by Quark Henares, Indie Manila, will expose the world of Independent Music in the Philippines, showcasing legendary and top indie rock bands.
